=Description=

"MOBA, meaning ‘self-build through mutual help’ enables lower income populations in the region to collectively access finance for affordable housing. Pilot projects under way in Budapest, Ljubljana, Belgrade and Zagreb show it can provide stable, affordable, socially owned housing. The institutional framework that MOBA is building offers a model for systemic transformation of local housing markets everywhere."

